ygData.messageBody:
Salutations Ainthara!

Welcome!

I'm kind of new here myself, and also still kind of
new to EQ as well. Just a couple months on line.

I tend to ask a lot of silly questions here on the
list, but that's because I like to chat and sometimes
can't seem to shut up.
:o)

I play a lvl 14 Wood Elv Ranger (Brangvyne) on Xegony
and a lvl 1 Shadown Knight Iksar (? - hehe cant
remember my name on the same server), though I have
not done much with her. I also have a lvl 1 Half Elf
Bard (Brangvyne) on the Cazin Thule (sp) server, but
again have not persued it much up to this point.

If you, or anyone on the list actually, bumps into me
please feel free to say hi.
:o)

Would love to chat with you about whatever anytime.

:o)
Brangvyne
